statements: SELECT id, item_name, item_code, quantity, location, usage_data FROM inventory_levels;
SELECT item_name, item_code, location, quantity, id, usage_data FROM inventory_levels;
SELECT item_name, quantity, usage_data, location, id, item_code FROM inventory_levels;
SELECT location, item_name, id, quantity, item_code, usage_data FROM inventory_levels;
SELECT id, item_name, quantity, usage_data, item_code, location FROM inventory_levels;
SELECT * FROM inventory_levels WHERE quantity > 100 ORDER BY item_name ASC, location DESC;
SELECT item_name, item_code, location FROM inventory_levels WHERE location = 'Warehouse A' ORDER BY item_code ASC;
SELECT item_name, quantity FROM inventory_levels WHERE quantity < 50 AND location LIKE '%Storage%' ORDER BY quantity DESC;
SELECT item_name, item_code, location FROM inventory_levels WHERE item_name ILIKE 'b%' AND quantity BETWEEN 50 AND 100 ORDER BY item_name;
SELECT item_name, location, quantity FROM inventory_levels WHERE item_code IN ('ABC123', 'DEF456', 'GHI789') ORDER BY location, quantity DESC;
SELECT * FROM inventory_supplies;
SELECT supply_name, quantity FROM inventory_supplies WHERE category = 'Electronics';
SELECT supply_id, supply_name, quantity FROM inventory_supplies ORDER BY supply_id ASC;
SELECT MAX(quantity) AS max_quantity FROM inventory_supplies;
SELECT sensor_id, sensor_location, last_recorded_date FROM sensor_data WHERE usage_count > 100;
SELECT * FROM inventory_supplies WHERE quantity > 100 ORDER BY last_usage_date DESC;
SELECT supply_name, category, quantity FROM inventory_supplies WHERE category = 'Electronics' AND quantity < 50 ORDER BY supply_name ASC;

SELECT sensor_location, supply_name, usage_count FROM sensor_data INNER JOIN inventory_supplies ON sensor_data.supply_id = inventory_supplies.supply_id WHERE usage_count > 500 ORDER BY usage_count DESC, sensor_location ASC;
SELECT MAX(quantity) AS max_quantity, MIN(quantity) AS min_quantity, AVG(quantity) AS avg_quantity FROM inventory_supplies;
SELECT supply_name, COUNT(*) AS total_records FROM inventory_supplies GROUP BY supply_name HAVING COUNT(*) > 3 ORDER BY total_records DESC;

SELECT supply_name, quantity FROM inventory_supplies ORDER BY quantity DESC;
SELECT supply_name, location, last_updated FROM inventory_supplies ORDER BY last_updated DESC;
SELECT * FROM inventory_supplies WHERE quantity > 0 ORDER BY last_updated DESC;
SELECT supply_name, quantity FROM inventory_supplies WHERE supply_name LIKE '%paper%' ORDER BY supply_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM sensor_data WHERE temperature > 30 AND humidity < 60 ORDER BY timestamp;
SELECT sensor_location, sensor_type FROM iot_sensors WHERE installation_date > '2021-01-01' ORDER BY sensor_location, sensor_type;
SELECT supply_name, location, last_updated FROM inventory_supplies WHERE location = 'Warehouse A' ORDER BY last_updated DESC;

SELECT sensor_type, COUNT(sensor_id) AS total_sensors FROM sensors GROUP BY sensor_type HAVING COUNT(sensor_id) > 1 ORDER BY total_sensors DESC;
SELECT supply_id, MAX(quantity_used) AS max_usage FROM usage_data GROUP BY supply_id ORDER BY max_usage DESC;
SELECT * FROM inventory ORDER BY item_name ASC;

SELECT sensor_type, location FROM sensor_data WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01' AND timestamp < '2022-02-01' ORDER BY sensor_id, timestamp DESC;

SELECT usage_id, category_name, quantity_used FROM usage_data INNER JOIN item_category ON usage_data.item_id = item_category.category_id WHERE quantity_used > 100 ORDER BY quantity_used DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT sensor_id, COUNT(DISTINCT location) AS num_locations FROM sensor_location GROUP BY sensor_id HAVING num_locations > 1 ORDER BY num_locations DESC;
